meta.about: We are a Chinese restaurant serving traditional Shanghainese cuisine.  Started in 2018, our first shop in Tokwawan was closed in July 2021.  We have now moved to the China Hong Kong City in Tsim Sha Tsui, which has started operation from November 2021.
